вЂЄ[stammers] Don't start.

187
00:10:04.750 --> 00:10:06.291
вЂЄDon't start with your shenanigans.

188
00:10:07.750 --> 00:10:08.750
вЂЄYou haven't even cooked.

189
00:10:08.833 --> 00:10:10.875
вЂЄ-Don't you cook in this house?
вЂЄ-[fridge door closes]

190
00:10:11.791 --> 00:10:12.833
вЂЄWhy didn't you cook?

191
00:10:16.333 --> 00:10:17.541
вЂЄListen here. Joyce.

192
00:10:18.458 --> 00:10:20.541
вЂЄAnd listen to me carefully. okay?

193
00:10:21.125 --> 00:10:22.791
вЂЄI want you to listen.

194
00:10:25.208 --> 00:10:26.416
вЂЄWhat's this?

195
00:10:30.166 --> 00:10:31.666
вЂЄ[ominous music playing]

196
00:10:32.875 --> 00:10:34.625
вЂЄ[Jonasi] I asked you a question.

197
00:10:35.208 --> 00:10:36.750
вЂЄWhat is this?

198
00:10:36.833 --> 00:10:38.041
вЂЄDon't shout.

199
00:10:38.125 --> 00:10:39.583
вЂЄ-I'm not shouting.
вЂЄ-Don't shout at me.

200
00:10:39.666 --> 00:10:41.000
вЂЄI asked you a question.

201
00:10:41.083 --> 00:10:43.375
вЂЄWhat are you trying to do?
вЂЄWhy did you do this?

202
00:10:44.041 --> 00:10:45.750
вЂЄWhat do you want from me?

203
00:10:45.833 --> 00:10:47.791
вЂЄWhat's the meaning of this?

204
00:10:47.875 --> 00:10:49.875
вЂЄWhy did you cut up our family photos?

205
00:10:49.958 --> 00:10:51.708
вЂЄI'm the one who cut those pictures.

206
00:10:51.791 --> 00:10:54.583
вЂЄ[chuckles] Would you like to know
вЂЄwhy I did that?

207
00:10:55.833 --> 00:10:58.750
вЂЄ-Because I hate you.
вЂЄ-[Joyce exhales]

208
00:11:00.500 --> 00:11:01.708
вЂЄYou hate me?

209
00:11:01.791 --> 00:11:03.125
вЂЄWhat's he doing here?

210
00:11:05.166 --> 00:11:06.916
вЂЄ-What are you doing here?
вЂЄ-Wow.

211
00:11:12.083 --> 00:11:13.583
вЂЄListen here. my boy.

212
00:11:14.416 --> 00:11:16.750
вЂЄThe crap you're asking me.

213
00:11:16.833 --> 00:11:19.875
вЂЄyou should ask me when
вЂЄyou have your own house. Understood?

214
00:11:19.958 --> 00:11:21.125
вЂЄMove out of my way.

215
00:11:21.833 --> 00:11:25.083
вЂЄ-[Mpume] That's what he's good at.
вЂЄ-You. You should discipline your children.

216
00:11:25.166 --> 00:11:26.958
вЂЄ-[chuckles]
вЂЄ-Understood?

217
00:11:27.041 --> 00:11:28.708
вЂЄTalk to your children.

218
00:11:30.166 --> 00:11:31.791
вЂЄ[Menzi] Fuck it. I've had enough of this.

219
00:11:31.875 --> 00:11:33.708
вЂЄ[footsteps departing]

220
00:11:38.333 --> 00:11:40.458
вЂЄ-There's no need at allвЂ¦
вЂЄ-Wow.

221
00:11:40.541 --> 00:11:41.875
вЂЄвЂ¦for you to get into bed.

222
00:11:43.125 --> 00:11:45.416
вЂЄNtombi prepared the guest room.

223
00:11:45.500 --> 00:11:46.500
вЂЄOh. wow.

224
00:11:46.583 --> 00:11:47.750
вЂЄGuest room?

225
00:11:48.625 --> 00:11:50.375
вЂЄThis is my house. Joyce.

226
00:11:51.500 --> 00:11:52.958
вЂЄI'm not a guest.

227
00:11:54.291 --> 00:11:56.000
вЂЄ[sighs. grunts]

228
00:11:57.458 --> 00:11:59.083
вЂЄ[sighs]

229
00:12:01.375 --> 00:12:03.583
вЂЄWhat did I ever do to you?

230
00:12:04.291 --> 00:12:06.666
вЂЄTo deserve such hate from you?

231
00:12:06.750 --> 00:12:10.625
вЂЄ[inhales]
вЂЄDespite all I've done. especially for you.

232
00:12:11.541 --> 00:12:14.500
вЂЄ-I still love you.
вЂЄ-Love shouldn't humiliate.

233
00:12:14.583 --> 00:12:17.458
вЂЄLove shouldn't hurt. Jonasi.

234
00:12:17.541 --> 00:12:19.541
вЂЄ[sighs] Here we go.

235
00:12:19.625 --> 00:12:23.833
вЂЄAnd all this time I've been
вЂЄdeluding myself. hoping that you and IвЂ¦

236
00:12:23.916 --> 00:12:27.958
вЂЄWe could somehow get back
вЂЄto the way we used to be.

237
00:12:29.166 --> 00:12:32.041
вЂЄBut I see that's not going to happen.

238
00:12:33.541 --> 00:12:35.250
вЂЄI want a divorce.

239
00:12:35.333 --> 00:12:37.708
вЂЄ[chuckles] That's not happening.

240
00:12:39.250 --> 00:12:42.416
вЂЄYou've depleted
вЂЄthe love I once had for you.

241
00:12:42.500 --> 00:12:46.125
вЂЄ-[Jonasi] Mmm.
вЂЄ-There's nothing left between you and I.

242
00:12:46.208 --> 00:12:48.250
вЂЄIt's over. I've had enough.

243
00:12:49.041 --> 00:12:51.541
вЂЄThe only way I'll be leaving

244
00:12:52.458 --> 00:12:57.000
вЂЄis the day when they put me
вЂЄin a coffin and bury me.

245
00:12:57.833 --> 00:12:59.791
вЂЄThat's when you will get rid of me.

246
00:13:01.541 --> 00:13:04.166
вЂЄ-[dramatic music playing]
вЂЄ-[fire crackling]

247
00:13:12.583 --> 00:13:14.625
вЂЄ-[footsteps approaching]
вЂЄ-[Joyce] Greetings.

248
00:13:15.375 --> 00:13:18.166
вЂЄYou know. Mom. I don't know
вЂЄif my eyes are deceiving me.

249
00:13:18.250 --> 00:13:20.416
вЂЄbut I think I see Jonasi over there.

250
00:13:21.000 --> 00:13:22.875
вЂЄ[Menzi] What the hell
вЂЄis he still doing here?

251
00:13:23.875 --> 00:13:26.208
вЂЄHe refused to leave.
вЂЄWhat was I supposed to do?

252
00:13:26.291 --> 00:13:29.750
вЂЄHe refused?
вЂЄWhat's so hard about calling the police?

253
00:13:29.833 --> 00:13:32.041
вЂЄ-Get a protection order.
вЂЄ-Hold on. Menzi.

254
00:13:32.125 --> 00:13:34.583
вЂЄDon't speak to me like that. Goodness.

255
00:13:34.666 --> 00:13:37.166
вЂЄThat man is a dog. You can't change that.

256
00:13:38.375 --> 00:13:40.208
вЂЄThings are going to be
вЂЄdifferent this time.

257
00:13:40.291 --> 00:13:42.875
вЂЄ-How. Mom?
вЂЄ-[clicks tongue]

258
00:13:42.958 --> 00:13:44.041
вЂЄ-[Joyce] Menzi.
вЂЄ-[Menzi] No. Mom.

259
00:13:44.125 --> 00:13:45.208
вЂЄExactly how. Mom?

260
00:13:45.291 --> 00:13:46.958
вЂЄMpume. [stammers]

261
00:13:47.041 --> 00:13:49.458
вЂЄOh. well. it's all up to you now.

262
00:13:52.166 --> 00:13:53.416
вЂЄ[Joyce] My gosh.

263
00:13:55.583 --> 00:13:56.958
вЂЄJoyce.

264
00:13:57.041 --> 00:13:59.208
вЂЄCan you see this marriage
вЂЄis going to kill you?

265
00:13:59.291 --> 00:14:01.791
вЂЄYou gave up your career.
вЂЄNow you're going to lose your kids.

266
00:14:01.875 --> 00:14:04.416
вЂЄMy god. Mom. please stop.

267
00:14:04.500 --> 00:14:06.666
вЂЄWhy are you tiptoeing around him. Joyce?

268
00:14:06.750 --> 00:14:08.625
вЂЄ-What do you want from him?
вЂЄ-[grunts]

269
00:14:15.625 --> 00:14:17.291
вЂЄ[pensive music playing]

270
00:14:20.875 --> 00:14:22.166
вЂЄ[exhales]

271
00:14:27.416 --> 00:14:30.583
вЂЄ-[Matipa] <i>вЂЄLife has put us through hell.</i>
вЂЄ-[Joyce scoffs]

272
00:14:31.166 --> 00:14:33.583
вЂЄAn STD. though. Matipa?

273
00:14:35.333 --> 00:14:36.833
