274
00:14:39.791 --> 00:14:42.250
вЂЄ[sighs] I'm such a fool.

275
00:14:42.333 --> 00:14:44.791
вЂЄYeah. that makes the two of us.

276
00:14:44.875 --> 00:14:48.958
вЂЄAs we're speaking. he's at home. lounging.

277
00:14:49.041 --> 00:14:50.416
вЂЄ-LoungingвЂ¦
вЂЄ-[sighs]

278
00:14:50.500 --> 00:14:54.666
вЂЄвЂ¦without any care.
вЂЄlike he's done nothing wrong.

279
00:14:54.750 --> 00:14:58.916
вЂЄYou now. I pray to God that he
вЂЄdoesn't even try to muster the courage

280
00:14:59.000 --> 00:15:01.708
вЂЄwith that ego of his
вЂЄto show up at my house

281
00:15:01.791 --> 00:15:03.958
вЂЄbecause I will honestly pour
вЂЄboiling water over him.

282
00:15:04.541 --> 00:15:06.083
вЂЄHe'll show up.

283
00:15:07.166 --> 00:15:09.000
вЂЄHe's also your husband. right?

284
00:15:09.083 --> 00:15:10.541
вЂЄHmm?

285
00:15:10.625 --> 00:15:13.583
вЂЄYou married him. [scoffs]

286
00:15:13.666 --> 00:15:17.916
вЂЄOne thing that is evidently clearвЂ¦

287
00:15:21.333 --> 00:15:24.416
вЂЄis that I'll never be enough for Jonasi.

288
00:15:25.583 --> 00:15:29.541
вЂЄI don't think anyone
вЂЄcan ever be enough for Jonasi.

289
00:15:30.125 --> 00:15:31.333
вЂЄ[Joyce scoffs]

290
00:15:32.666 --> 00:15:34.541
вЂЄ-[crickets chirping]
вЂЄ-[dog barking]

291
00:15:35.375 --> 00:15:36.833
вЂЄ[knife chopping]

292
00:15:53.125 --> 00:15:55.541
вЂЄ[suspenseful music playing]

293
00:16:49.958 --> 00:16:51.041
вЂЄ[Jonasi] Wow.

294
00:16:52.375 --> 00:16:54.583
вЂЄ[ominous music playing]

295
00:16:54.666 --> 00:16:55.791
вЂЄMmm.

296
00:16:55.875 --> 00:16:58.041
вЂЄ[chuckles] Mmm.

297
00:16:59.583 --> 00:17:03.208
вЂЄ-Delicious. Mmm.
вЂЄ-[Joyce chuckles]

298
00:17:03.708 --> 00:17:04.708
вЂЄ[Jonasi] Oh. wow.

299
00:17:06.000 --> 00:17:07.000
вЂЄMmm.

300
00:17:08.458 --> 00:17:10.000
вЂЄ[music continues]

301
00:17:11.291 --> 00:17:12.833
вЂЄ[Jonasi sighs]

302
00:17:15.166 --> 00:17:16.166
вЂЄMm-hmm.

303
00:17:19.000 --> 00:17:20.000
вЂЄMmm.

304
00:17:20.083 --> 00:17:22.333
вЂЄThis is what they mean when they say

305
00:17:22.416 --> 00:17:26.666
вЂЄa way to a man's heart
вЂЄis through his stomach.

306
00:17:27.458 --> 00:17:29.708
вЂЄThere we go. There we go.

307
00:17:34.458 --> 00:17:35.875
вЂЄ[sighs] Mpume.

308
00:17:36.458 --> 00:17:37.958
вЂЄBaby. please wait.

309
00:17:38.041 --> 00:17:39.041
вЂЄWow.

310
00:17:39.125 --> 00:17:41.375
вЂЄIt's late now.
вЂЄCan't you reconsider staying for a day?

311
00:17:41.458 --> 00:17:43.666
вЂЄ-Mm-mmm. No. no.
вЂЄ-Two max.

312
00:17:43.750 --> 00:17:44.916
вЂЄ[sighs]

313
00:17:45.000 --> 00:17:46.250
вЂЄYou're disappointing me.

314
00:17:53.791 --> 00:17:54.916
вЂЄI'll be all right.

315
00:17:55.458 --> 00:17:59.916
вЂЄI'm staying at a friend's house.
вЂЄFrom there. I head to Stellenbosch.

316
00:18:00.708 --> 00:18:05.625
вЂЄI know I've mentioned this before.
вЂЄbut I need you to hear me.

317
00:18:05.708 --> 00:18:06.750
вЂЄAll right?

318
00:18:07.458 --> 00:18:11.333
вЂЄI'm going to fix this.
вЂЄOne way or the other.

319
00:18:11.416 --> 00:18:12.666
вЂЄOkay?

320
00:18:12.750 --> 00:18:14.250
вЂЄTrust me.

321
00:18:14.750 --> 00:18:16.375
вЂЄPlease remember.

322
00:18:16.458 --> 00:18:21.833
вЂЄeverything I'm doing
вЂЄis for you and your brothers.

323
00:18:21.916 --> 00:18:22.916
вЂЄAndвЂ¦

324
00:18:24.000 --> 00:18:25.291
вЂЄI love you.

325
00:18:27.125 --> 00:18:28.791
вЂЄMore than anything.

326
00:18:30.333 --> 00:18:31.541
вЂЄ-Yeah?
вЂЄ-Mmm.

327
00:18:33.333 --> 00:18:34.375
вЂЄOkay.

328
00:18:36.958 --> 00:18:38.958
вЂЄI'll call you. okay?

329
00:18:41.458 --> 00:18:44.041
вЂЄ-Okay.
вЂЄ-It's getting late. Mom.

330
00:18:47.791 --> 00:18:50.541
вЂЄ[sniffles] I'll call you when I get there.

331
00:18:50.625 --> 00:18:51.666
вЂЄOkay.

332
00:18:54.250 --> 00:18:55.708
вЂЄSafe travels.

333
00:18:55.791 --> 00:18:56.958
вЂЄBye. Mama.

334
00:19:02.833 --> 00:19:04.083
вЂЄ[car beeps]

335
00:19:04.166 --> 00:19:08.458
вЂЄ-[car door opens. closes]
вЂЄ-[engine starts]

336
00:19:08.541 --> 00:19:09.541
