337
00:19:10.666 --> 00:19:11.916
вЂЄWhat are you doing?

338
00:19:12.000 --> 00:19:13.250
вЂЄ-[chuckles]
вЂЄ-Hmm?

339
00:19:13.333 --> 00:19:15.083
вЂЄ-What are you doing? [chuckles]
вЂЄ-We're playing.

340
00:19:15.166 --> 00:19:16.291
вЂЄ-Hey?
вЂЄ-[Joyce] You're playing?

341
00:19:16.375 --> 00:19:17.875
вЂЄ-[chuckles] Yeah.
вЂЄ-I see.

342
00:19:17.958 --> 00:19:19.250
вЂЄ-Mom. what are you doing?
вЂЄ-[Joyce] Oh. stop.

343
00:19:19.333 --> 00:19:21.458
вЂЄ-I'm asking if you connected here?
вЂЄ-[Menzi] It's connected.

344
00:19:21.541 --> 00:19:22.833
вЂЄ-Okay.
вЂЄ-[typing]

345
00:19:22.916 --> 00:19:24.625
вЂЄI want us to dance.

346
00:19:24.708 --> 00:19:26.416
вЂЄ-Mm-hmm.
вЂЄ-[Menzi chuckles] Come on. No ways.

347
00:19:26.500 --> 00:19:28.125
вЂЄRemember how we used to dance
вЂЄwhen we were young?

348
00:19:28.208 --> 00:19:29.708
вЂЄ-[Menzi] Ah. Mom. [chuckles]
вЂЄ-Huh?

349
00:19:29.791 --> 00:19:31.000
вЂЄ["Paradise Road" playing on speaker]

350
00:19:31.083 --> 00:19:32.666
вЂЄ-[chuckling]
вЂЄ-No way. No. no. No way.

351
00:19:32.750 --> 00:19:34.208
вЂЄCome on. No. Don't be a bore.

352
00:19:34.291 --> 00:19:36.333
вЂЄ-Get up. Come show me.
вЂЄ-Come on. Why?

353
00:19:36.416 --> 00:19:38.416
вЂЄDo you remember how we used to dance? Huh?

354
00:19:38.500 --> 00:19:40.125
вЂЄRemember when you were young?

355
00:19:40.208 --> 00:19:41.333
вЂЄ-No. Mom.
вЂЄ-Do you remember?

356
00:19:41.416 --> 00:19:44.458
вЂЄ["Paradise Road" continues. muffled]

357
00:19:53.416 --> 00:19:54.416
вЂЄ[sighs]

358
00:19:54.500 --> 00:19:58.041
вЂЄ[Joyce laughs]

359
00:19:58.125 --> 00:20:01.041
вЂЄLet's dance. boy!

360
00:20:01.125 --> 00:20:03.708
вЂЄ-[chuckles] Let's dance!
вЂЄ-Come on. Mom.

361
00:20:04.291 --> 00:20:05.708
вЂЄ[voicemail] <i>вЂЄHi. this is Essie.</i>

362
00:20:05.791 --> 00:20:07.500
<i>вЂЄ-I can't take your call right now.</i>
вЂЄ-[grunts]

363
00:20:11.333 --> 00:20:13.166
вЂЄ-[grunts]
вЂЄ-[line ringing]

364
00:20:13.250 --> 00:20:16.250
вЂЄ[voicemail] <i>вЂЄHi. this is Lindani.</i>
<i>вЂЄPlease leave a message.</i>

365
00:20:16.333 --> 00:20:18.583
вЂЄ-[Joyce chuckling] Yes!
вЂЄ-[Menzi chuckling]

366
00:20:18.666 --> 00:20:19.833
вЂЄ[all chuckling]

367
00:20:21.250 --> 00:20:23.458
вЂЄ-[all chuckling]
вЂЄ-[Joyce] My boy!

368
00:20:23.958 --> 00:20:25.458
вЂЄ[groans]

369
00:20:26.583 --> 00:20:27.791
вЂЄ[retching]

370
00:20:29.375 --> 00:20:30.375
вЂЄ[groans]

371
00:20:31.583 --> 00:20:33.125
вЂЄ[groaning]

372
00:20:33.208 --> 00:20:35.875
вЂЄ["Paradise Road" continues]

373
00:20:36.666 --> 00:20:39.375
вЂЄ[groans. echoes]

374
