378
00:20:55.416 --> 00:20:57.166
вЂЄ-It's their thing. Don't mind them.
вЂЄ-[Menzi chuckles]

379
00:20:57.250 --> 00:20:59.833
вЂЄ-Ma'am! Joyce!
вЂЄ-[groaning]

380
00:20:59.916 --> 00:21:01.625
вЂЄ-Mpume!
вЂЄ-[splutters. coughs]

381
00:21:01.708 --> 00:21:04.208
вЂЄ-Mr. Gomora! Mr. Gomora!
вЂЄ-[groans]

382
00:21:04.291 --> 00:21:06.500
вЂЄMa'am. come!

383
00:21:06.583 --> 00:21:09.208
вЂЄ-Sir. what's wrong? Oh. no!
вЂЄ-[groaning]

384
00:21:09.291 --> 00:21:10.500
вЂЄ[Sis Ntombi wails]

385
00:21:10.583 --> 00:21:12.833
вЂЄ["Paradise Road" continues]

386
00:21:18.208 --> 00:21:19.708
вЂЄ[Nkazimulo laughing. distorted]

387
00:21:25.291 --> 00:21:26.291
вЂЄ[laughter continues]

388
00:21:30.541 --> 00:21:32.583
вЂЄ["Paradise Road" continues]
